@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wamfua(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v0 - wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.18)))
    tmp = 0.31
    tmp = (v2 / wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.12)))
    v2 = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.53 * v2 + 0.01) - (tmp + 0.84 * v0 + 0.33)))
    data[tid] = v0
